<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { background-color: #0284c7; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .order-details { margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 20px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; }
        th, td { padding: 8px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for shopping with ElectroStore! Your order has been received and is currently being processed.</p>
            
            <div class="order-details">
                <h3>Order #{{orderId}}</h3>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Item</th>
                            <th>Qty</th>
                            <th>Price</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {{#each items}}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{this.productName}}</td>
                            <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                            <td>${{this.price}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        {{/each}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <p style="text-align: right; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;">Total: ${{total}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>We'll notify you once your package is shipped.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The ElectroStore Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 ElectroStore. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
